
# Virtual Reality --> House

Blender + ThreeJS + WebGL

## Installation

  `$ npm install && cd public npm install && bower install && grunt build`

And then run:

  `$ npm start`

## Usage

Run --> http://localhost:5000

``
C -> Aerial View
B -> Exit Aerial View

Arrow keys -> left/right/forward/backward
U -> Ascend
J -> Descend

abhimanyuarya [3:36 PM]
On mouse click and move : rotate view

Zoom only in aerial view through mouse scroll
``

